{"tid":5444,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"賞茶同茶湯會有得揮","createTime":"2016-11-27T02:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-28T05:36:51.000Z","uid":16652,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"563ab48e5df1c1f0fad61dd7009d2c1e6d74e783","tid":5444,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T02:03:14.000Z","msg":"行過見到灣仔開左間咁嘅嘢。。。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a63BS7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa63BS7.jpg&h=acdae6b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇個樣以為係文青x冥茶x伏伏地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢寫住波霸奶奶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我最鍾意大奶奶所以決定去朝下性 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫左半糖因爲我係肥婆<br />\n再肥我驚蘋果訪問我嗰陣會怕醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/476831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F476831.jpg&h=29ea1f8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n發現左有舊被安樂死嘅青檸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/89r1TA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F89r1TA.jpg&h=54b74930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n半料都幾甜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但珍珠係彈牙嘅<br />\n係又多又細粒但梗唔死我嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又真係幾好飲各位大佬可以去一戰嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba761ba44e43bbbd38ec7ad60b16f8f940cc43b","tid":5444,"uid":27575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T02:31:47.000Z","msg":"打手"},{"pid":"58ec27cc24a93988d4186c96d2fa560364f6ef9e","tid":5444,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,